(21, 1, '2014-07-07 14:55:18', '2014-07-07 21:55:18', '<h2>We are Building a Global Movement to Protect the Free and Open Web</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Mozilla’s Open Web Policy program</strong> is aimed at advancing and protecting the free and open web. We''re helping the global network of <strong>developers, makers and organizers</strong> create tools and programs to enable organizations to help shape policy, and <strong>policy makers</strong> to understand the impact of their policy on the Internet.</p>\r\n', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-07-28 15:10:31', '2014-07-28 22:10:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mozilla/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
