(77, 1, '2014-07-17 14:55:04', '2014-07-17 21:55:04', '<h3>We are Building a Global Movement to Protect the Free and Open Web</h3>\r\nMozilla’s Open Web Policy program is aimed at advancing and protecting the free and open web. We’re helping the global network of developers, makers and organizers create tools and programs to enable organizations to help shape policy, and policy makers to understand the impact of their policy on the Internet.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-17 14:55:04', '2014-07-17 21:55:04', '', 21, 'http://localhost/mozilla/2014/07/17/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
