ations</h4>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://publicknowledge.org"><img src="http://localhost/mozilla/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/Public-Knowledge.png" alt="Public-Knowledge" width="250" height="39" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-150" /></a> <a href="http://amnesty.org"><img src="http://localhost/mozilla/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/amnesty.jpg" alt="amnesty" width="250" height="106" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-121" /></a> <a href="http://freepress.net"><img src="http://localhost/mozilla/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/freepress.jpg" alt="freepress" width="250" height="109" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-123" /></a> <a href="http://oti.newamerica.net"><img src="http://localhost/mozilla/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/oti.jpg" alt="oti" width="250" height="75" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-124" /></a> <a href="https://www.aclu.org/"><img src="http://localhost/mozilla/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/acluf.jpg" alt="acluf" width="250" height="94" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-125" /></a>\r\n\r\n<small>Photo: Elvert Barnes via Flickr</small>', 'Open Web Fellows', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-25 16:14:37', '2014-07-25 23:14:37', '', 6, 'http://localhost/mozilla/2014/07/25/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
