(171, 1, '2014-07-28 14:26:25', '2014-07-28 21:26:25', '<h2>We are Building a Global Movement to Protect the Free and Open Web</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Mozilla’s Open Web Policy program</strong> is aimed at advancing and protecting the free and open web. We''re helping the global network of <strong>developers, makers and organizers</strong> create tools and programs to enable organizations to help shape policy, and <strong>policy makers</strong> to understand the impact of their policy on the Internet.</p>\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-28 14:26:25', '2014-07-28 21:26:25', '', 21, 'http://localhost/mozilla/2014/07/28/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
